metadata.name: Mutum
metadata.description:
An African man is a proud man, who takes pride in his family, an African man is a man of duty, he takes honor in service, service to his woman, his children, and his community, to protect, provide, love, care and put everyone before himself. Mutum is an African man. 

A scene in IGA FULANI ( Fulani Settlement ) far Ibadan Nigeria, the Fulani are a tribe across Africa, a large number of these tribes live in absence of civilization, being cattle herders is their main source of living...
